::Frightened but determined the man confronts you.::

Damn you, $(#man/woman)! You... you killed all my friends! I never wanted to do this, but it's the only way now... I can't let the Protectorate win! The Free Drones will fight on!
Why are you doing this? Are you this wil (0971722b-df55-45b2-a2b0-7a448520c60f)
Why are you doing this? Are you this willing to blow yourself up only to deprive the Protectorate of some supplies?

::[Intimidate]:: You are not dying today. Either defuse the bomb and walk a free man, or I'll make sure I drag you far away from the blast and into the hands of men who will gladly make the rest of your life nothing but pure, unadulterated agony.
Stop wasting my time. Move aside! (3def5782-e00a-4f89-8b8f-3defbff27271)
Stop wasting my time. Move aside!
I'm a Free Drone, that's who I am! And I (a120d963-544c-45dd-b701-223e682c86b3)

I'm a Free Drone, that's who I am! And I am eager to give my life to make *sure* those Protectorate cans are driven out of this world. They have a powerful army, they have their mighty Dreadnoughts, but we have the courage and the will to resist them... and their devious manipulations.
